From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 28 Jun 2026 17:51:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] Phase A2+B: learning engine test suite and redesigned
 Performance page
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

A2 — Test suite (160 tests, 0 failures):
- Added vitest with full test coverage across failure-classifier,
  match-review, learning-signals, exact-score-analysis,
  recommendation-insight, decision-support, integration, golden
  matches, benchmarks, and regression paths
- Shared test-factories.ts with fully-typed factory helpers
- Fixed production bugs: duplicate const in failure-classifier,
  missing over_predicted_goals lesson in match-review

Phase B — Performance page redesign:
- Replaced monolithic AnalysisPanel with PerformancePanel + 6 tabs
- Decision Review: match-by-match review with pts/delta summary
- Override Intelligence: win rate, delta, and history table
- Engine Learning: derived signals with strength and active status
- Blind Spots: failure pattern breakdown with visual bars
- Exact Score Optimisation: distribution, bias, missed patterns
- Diagnostics: model leaderboard, calibration, health (existing views)
- All tabs consume A1/A2 lib layer; no new migrations, no UI regressions

